{"tid":2457296,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國Rapper Keith Ape 親自宣佈壽命只剩不到六個月","createTime":"2021-03-22T13:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T13:51:07.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6f2602efa423031e911a12bb84ffea351a1418","tid":2457296,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.billboard.com/files/media/keith-ape-2018-cr-nigel-powers-billboard-1548-compressed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.billboard.com%2Ffiles%2Fmedia%2Fkeith-ape-2018-cr-nigel-powers-billboard-1548-compressed.jpg&h=d37c99cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自韓國知名饒舌歌手 Keith Ape 因與 KOHH、Loota 等人合作的傳奇饒舌歌曲《It G Ma》廣為人知，隨後無論是自己的作品或是與其他歌手的重磅組合也都引起樂迷廣大迴響，然而稍早，Keith Ape 在個人 Instagram 上正式宣佈他被醫生診斷，自身壽命因為疾病即將終結。<br />\n<br />\nKeith Ape 並沒有表明罹患了什麼樣的病症和原因，他在貼文中寫道：「對我的 Hater 來說這是個好消息。我的醫生告訴我，我只剩下三到六個月的生命，我想和影響我音樂事業的人做們做一些事，或者和我敬佩的藝術家寫首歌，在我離開這個星球之前，我想盡可能地留下我的音樂作品」。Keith Ape 希望將自己殘留的生命獻給音樂。<br />\n<br />\nKeith Ape 現在僅 27 歲，樂迷們十分擔心他可能會成為「27 Club」一員，現在只能祈求 Keith Ape 一切順利，更多後續報導還請持許留意 HYPEBEAST。"},{"pid":"48ba9b4a081f19ad42fa781a7afdfcfe4665434b","tid":2457296,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hypebeast.com/zh/2021/3/keith-ape-life-expectancy-several-months-news%3famp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2021%2F3%2Fkeith-ape-life-expectancy-several-months-news%253famp%3D1&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXN9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=bccd26f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hypebeast.com/zh/2021/3/keith-ape-life-expectancy-several-months-news%3famp=1</a>"}]}